Akken daɣen i tedṛa d imezdaɣ n temdinin n Sudum d Gumuṛ akk-d tudrin i sent-id-yezzin, ixeddmen anagar ticmatin d zzna, qqiment-ed d lemtel mi tent-yessenger Sidi Ṛebbi s tmes yecban times n ǧahennama ;
ur sɛin ara ayen ara teččem d wayen ara teswem akk-d wayen ara teswem neɣ imi ur tettabaɛem ara ayen yeɛnan leɛyudat, talalit n waggur d wussan n westeɛfu ;
Akken daɣen i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen. Cban itran ixețțin, iɣellin ɣer dderb n ṭṭlam i sen ițwaheggan.
Asirem-agi d ayen yeṭṭfen tudert-nneɣ am umextaf ( tnejga ) yeṭṭfen lbabuṛ, yețɛedday akkin i leḥjab ɣer wemkan iqedsen,
Dexxan n tmes s wayes ara nɛețțaben ad yeqqim si lǧil ɣer lǧil ; wid yețseǧǧiden zdat leɛqiṛa d lmeṣuɛ ines akk-d kra win iqeblen ticṛeṭ n isem-is, ur steɛfayen ara iḍ d wass.
Sṭamaɛen anagar yir tilawin iwakken ad znun yid-sent ; ur ɛeggun ara di ddnubat i xeddmen, țɣuṛṛun imdanen ur neǧhid ara di liman, ččuṛen d ṭṭmeɛ, ț-țarwa n deɛwessu.
A ten-tɛeqlem s lecɣal-nsen. UUr d-nțekkes ara tiẓurin seg inijel, neɣ lexṛif seg isennanen.
Iḍ wis ṛbeɛṭac, mazal aḍu yețhuccu-yaɣ ițțawi-yaɣ akkin akka ɣef lebḥeṛ Agrakal ; di țnaṣfa n yiḍ, ibeḥṛiyen ḥussen belli ur bɛiden ara ɣef lberr.
Ayen akk i d-iteṭṭfen deg umenɣi, d ayen i d-ideṛṛun di mkul amkan n lḥekma, akk-d țmettilen-d igduden, wid iwumi d-yessawel Sidi Ṛebbi s wul yeṣfan. Yella daɣen wid iwumi i d-yessawel Sidi Ṛebbi mačči s ɣuṛ-sen.
Deg yiwet n teswiɛt, tekker-ed tbuciḍant di lebḥeṛ armi tɣumm teflukt-nni s lemwaji. Sidna Ɛisa yella iṭṭes. Deg wexxam-nni i deg ilaq ad iṛuḥ ad iqdiren ɣer rrif n tmura n Surya.
M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq, ur tețțen ara alamma uɣen luḍu. ?ṭfen daɣen deg waṭas n lɛaddat nniḍen : tarda n yeqbac, n tbuqalin, akk-d lḥilat meṛṛa n nnḥas.
?ef ddemma n wannect-agi i gețṛaǧu deg-wen ad yili d sebba s wayes ara yilin d sebba n tuccḍa neɣ d wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ ; wid akk ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ, nhiɣ-ten ad yili d wussan n lekdeb. ?ef wannect-agi i d-yessefhem ayen i d-tenna ccariɛa, i gețṛaǧu deg-wen Sidi Ṛebbi, ad yili d sebba n lḥeqq akk-d țmanegt si tejmaɛt.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
Lameɛna a sen-naru tabṛaț iwakken ad ṭṭixṛen ɣef wučči n weksum immezlen i lmeṣnuɛat d ssadat. Ad ttixṛen daɣen i yir tikli, i wučči n lmal immurḍsen akk-d tissit n idammen,
Akken daɣen i tedṛa d imezdaɣ n temdinin n Sudum d Gumuṛ akk-d tudrin i sent-id-yezzin, ixeddmen anagar ticmatin d zzna, qqiment-ed d lemtel mi tent-yessenger Sidi Ṛebbi s tmes yecban times n ǧahennama ;
?waṛejmen, țwajeṛben, țwagezmen s umencaṛ, mmuten s ujenwi, teddun sya ɣer da, llebsa nsen d ibḍanen n wulli ț-țɣeṭṭen, yețwakkes-asen kullec, țwaḥeqṛen, țwaqehṛen.
A d-nefk lemtel n dduzan n lmusiqa am tjewwaqt d snitra : ma yella ur yemxalaf ara ṣṣut-nsent, amek ara neɛqel ṣṣut n tjewaqt neɣ win n snitra ?
Akken daɣen taṣebḥit, teqqaṛem a d-iwwet ugeffur ( lehwa ) axaṭer yella usigna. AAmek ! Tesnem aț-țfehmem lḥala n igenni, ur tezmirem ara aț-țfehmem licaṛat yeɛnan lweqt-agi !
